Module Cryptography

Package cryptography.cracking

This package contains utilities for cracking encrypted messages. You probably do not need to use it manually, as this is already implemented in the according classes.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Crackable
    This interface provides ciphers the ability to crack an unknown encrypted message.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Candidate
    This class represents a solution for a cracked cipher.
    SpellChecker
    This class represents a spell checker.
